      <div class="beu-data-text">
        January 2026 alone. The highest January total since the financial crisis. 
        <strong>AI was cited in 7,624 of those cuts.</strong> 
        And 92% of Fortune 500 companies have adopted AI — but only 5-6% have scaled it. 
        <strong>You're seeing the tip of the iceberg.</strong>
